@BrigetteRomanek's interiors are evocative of lived-in elegance. “That is everything for me,” she says. In her own home, she displays $2 flea-market vases next to pieces that cost hundreds of times as much. ✨ Tap the link in our bio to shop Brigette's curation for our latest edition of The Tastemaker's Edit. A portion of the proceeds benefits @Baby2Baby, which provides diapers and other essentials to children in need.

#TheTastemakersEdit #BrigetteRomanek #OneKingsLane
